# data files
# All working data lives in runtime-data/ (multi-GB, never committed) or in
# Postgres. `data`, `etl`, and `scripts` are local convenience symlinks.
# See docs/data-storage.md for the full strategy.
runtime-data/
/data
/etl
/scripts

